
Installing pySiLibUSB
=====================================

- libusb library: http://www.libusb.org/
  Linux:   from distribution
  Windows: http://libusb-win32.sourceforge.net/ or http://libusbx.org/
  OSX:     http://www.ellert.se/twain-sane/ or "sudo port install libusb" using macports
  
- PyUSB: https://github.com/walac/pyusb
  Installing from Python Package Index (PyPI):
  pip install pyusb

- Installing pySiLibUSB:
  python setup.py install

